message:
Happy to have met Indian & Kenyan business leaders with President Uhuru Kenyatta to chalk out ways to deepen India-Kenya economic & trade ties. 

Expressed support to ‘Make it Kenya' initiative & said that India stands firmly with Kenya as it works to strengthen the nation’s economy. India-Kenya friendship is a win-win situation. Earlier we fought colonialism…now is the time to fight poverty. http://nm-4.com/5hps
